ness and residential electric customers and more than  gas customers in an economically diverse squaremile area encompassing baltimore city and all or part of  central maryland counties today we are building on this proud tradition to create a promising future for our employees and our customers on may   constellation energy group began operations as the holding company for bge and its affiliates the creation of constellation energy group increases our opportunities and strengthens our ability to compete with energy companies across the nation on july   the company moved from being a vertically integrated utility that both produces and delivers electricity to one that delivers electricity produced by others  much as it already did for the natural gas side of the business upload an event to display on this page  savings breakdown greenhouse gas emissions  lbs pledge actions  dollars  kwh  btus  see pledges by action item member organizations show other members organization name  contribution lbs of greenhouse gases aeroseal of virginia  archived campaign success select a campaign year « select »         results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change the world campaign  greenhouse gas emissions lbs  dollars  kwh  btus  results for change a light campaign   of pledges   of bulbs  energy savings  kwh cost savings  greenhouse gas  lbs all organizations  energy star homepage header links 