june    in baltimore maryland founder rembrandt peale  headquarters baltimore maryland united states area served baltimore metropolitan area key people calvin g butler jr services electric power transmission parent exelon corporation nyse exc website wwwbgecom baltimore gas and electric company bge is a subsidiary of the exelon corporation and maryland’s largest gas and electric utility bge earlier had created the holding company constellation energy in  constellation energy was acquired by exelon in  headquartered in baltimore bge provides service to more than  million electric customers and more than  natural gas customers in central maryland bge employs  people in the state of maryland making the company one of the  largest private employers in the region contents  history  operations  community  references historyedit this section needs expansion you can help by adding to it june  artist  sculptor museum operator rembrandt peale  incorporated the gas light company of baltimore on june   after having exhibited gas lighting at his holliday street museum which was designed by famed local architect robert cary long jr built and opened in  between east saratoga and east lexington streets  after a variety of uses including as baltimores city hall  later in  to become the municipal museum of the city of baltimore popularly known once again as the peale museum into   this was the first gas company in the americas the first streetlamp installed by the gas light company of baltimore stood at the corner of north holliday and east baltimore streets and was lit on february th  by february of  only  gaslit lamps existed the belvidere theatre became the first public building to be lit using gas over the next decades the company experimented with piping meters and other mechanical technology baltimore committed to gas for municipal use including the installation of gas service in all public markets between by  private subscription also steadily increased by  the company had  cu